# Redirect non-www to www (301 permanent redirects)
https://learnbyshorts.com/* https://www.learnbyshorts.com/:splat 301!
http://learnbyshorts.com/* https://www.learnbyshorts.com/:splat 301!

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS for www
http://www.learnbyshorts.com/* https://www.learnbyshorts.com/:splat 301!

# Specific page redirects (in case Google has indexed specific old URLs)
/index.html https://www.learnbyshorts.com/ 301!
/about https://www.learnbyshorts.com/about.html 301!
/contact https://www.learnbyshorts.com/contact.html 301!
/design-patterns https://www.learnbyshorts.com/design-patterns.html 301!
